  "description": "Olivier salad is known as Russian salad outside of Russia. It is an essential part of the Russian New Year’s Eve feast. This recipe is using chicken (feel free to skip it for a vegetarian variation) instead of beef, which would be more common, and [homemade mayonnaise](https://tacohuaco.co/recipes/mayonnaise/) that gives it a very nice light olive flavor, in comparison to most store-bought mayonnaise with its unpleasant fattiness.",
